afatis]]||[[Korinthos F.C.|Korinthos]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Ntinos Konstantakis]]||[[Olympiakos Chersonissos F.C.|Chersonissos]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Stelios Maistrellis]]||[[Lamia F.C.|Lamia]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Yiorghos Manousos]]||[[OFI Crete|OFI]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|BIH}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Branislav Niki\u0107</span>||[[Panetolikos F.C.|Panetolikos]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Tasos Pappas]]||\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Vaggelis Pitkas]]||[[Anagennisi Karditsa F.C.|Anagennisi Karditsa]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Kyriakos Samaras</span>||\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Yiorghos Vourghountzis]]||[[OFI Crete|OFI]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Aris Xevghenis]]||[[Koropi F.C.|Koropi]]\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Dhimitris Yiovanakis]]||\n|-\n| Summer 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Dhimitris Zouliotis]]||[[Korinthos F.C.|Korinthos]]\n|-\n| 24 October 2008||{{flagicon|CRO}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Bojan Milovanovi\u0107</span>||\n|-\n| 7 December 2008||{{flagicon|SLO}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Dejan Bo\u017ei\u010di\u010d</span>||\n|-\n| 22 December 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Yiannis Mitseas</span>||[[Asteras Tripoli F.C.|Asteras Tripoli]]\n|-\n| 22 December 2008||{{flagicon|CRO}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Ivan Rasi\u0107</span>||\n|-\n| 22 December 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Apostolos Tsianakas]]||[[Fostiras F.C.|Fostiras]]\n|-\n| 29 December 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Yiorghos Tsetiroklis</span>||<span style=\"color:#003399\">Niki Polygyros</span>\n|-\n| 31 December 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} <span style=\"color:#003399\">Ghrighoris Christodoulou</span>||<span style=\"color:#003399\">Diagoras Aghia Paraskevi</span>\n|-\n| 31 December 2008||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Petros Dhalambekis]]||<span style=\"color:#003399\">Doxa Aspropyrgos-Panaspropyrgiako