]] {{goal|45}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|19 October 2008\n|[[Fostiras F.C.|Fostiras]]\n|[[Tavros|A]]\n|1&ndash;4\n|<span style=\"color:#003399\">Rasi\u0107</span> {{goal|35}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|26 October 2008\n|[[Ag. Dimitrios F.C.|Agios Dimitrios]]\n|[[Mytilene Municipal Stadium|H]]\n|0&ndash;3\n|\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|2 November 2008\n|[[Rodos F.C.|Rodos]]\n|[[Rhodes (city)|A]]\n|1&ndash;2\n|<span style=\"color:#003399\">Sofianis</span> {{goal|45}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|9 November 2008\n|[[Panachaiki 2005 F.C.|Panachaiki 2005]]\n|[[Mytilene Municipal Stadium|H]]\n|1&ndash;2\n|[[Petros Dhalambekis|Dhalambekis]] {{goal|63}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|16 November 2008\n|[[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]]\n|[[Stavros Mavrothalassitis Stadium|A]]\n|2&ndash;3\n|<span style=\"color:#003399\">Mandhilis</span> {{goal|49}}, <span style=\"color:#003399\">Dhimakis</span> {{goal|61}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\"\n|30 November 2008\n|[[Aias Salamina F.C.|Aias Salamina]]\n|[[Salamina (city)|A]]\n|1&ndash;1\n|[[Petros Dhalambekis|Dhalambekis]] {{goal|39}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"\n|7 December 2008\n|[[Ilioupoli F.C.|Ilioupoli]]\n|[[Mytilene Municipal Stadium|H]]\n|1&ndash;0\n|<span style=\"color:#003399\">Sofianis</span> {{goal|18}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\"\n|14 December 2008\n|[[Chaidari F.C.|Chaidari]]\n|[[Mytilene Municipal Stadium|H]]\n|1&ndash;0\n|<span style=\"color:#003399\">Papakostas</span> {{goal|86}}\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|17 December 2008<sup>+</sup>\n|[[Atsalenios F.C.|Atsalenios]]\n|[[Mytilene Municipal Stadium|H]]\n|0&ndash;2\n|\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|21 December 2008\n|[[Keravnos Keratea F.C.|Keravnos]]\n|[[Keratea|A]]\n|0&ndash;3\n|\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|&ndash;\n|[[Korinthos F.C.|Korinthos]]\n|\n|0&ndash;3\n|without match\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|&ndash;\n|[[Neos Asteras Rethymno F.C.|Neos Asteras Rethymno]]\n|\n|0&ndash;3\n|without match\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\"\n|&ndash;\n|[[Olympiakos Chersonissos F.C.|Chersonissos]]\n|\n|0&ndash;3\n|without match\n|- b